a pet or not?

528
00:34:12,240 --> 00:34:15,233
No, it's just me.

529
00:34:34,240 --> 00:34:36,391
Why do you let her
talk to you like that?

530
00:34:36,480 --> 00:34:38,392
She's not that bad.

531
00:34:38,480 --> 00:34:41,154
Son, she compared
you to a clam.

532
00:34:43,320 --> 00:34:44,834
Well, what should I do?

533
00:34:44,920 --> 00:34:47,879
A guy insulted me once.

534
00:34:47,960 --> 00:34:51,078
I pissed in his gas tank.

535
00:34:51,160 --> 00:34:53,516
