536
00:35:16,440 --> 00:35:17,874
<i>Leroy's Motor Inn.</i>

537
00:35:18,640 --> 00:35:19,596
Yes, ma'am.

538
00:35:19,720 --> 00:35:23,157
I'm looking out my window,
and there's a young fellow

539
00:35:23,240 --> 00:35:26,950
urinating in the gas
