552
00:36:06,880 --> 00:36:08,837
Hey there, Molly. Lou.

553
00:36:08,920 --> 00:36:10,149
Coffee?
Sure.

554
00:36:10,240 --> 00:36:11,356
Eggs over medium?

555
00:36:11,480 --> 00:36:12,516
Won't say no.

556
00:36:12,600 --> 00:36:14,319
How's the leg?

557
00:36:14,440 --> 00:36:17,638
Goes from my ass to
the ground just like the other.

558
00:36:17,720 --> 00:36:19,313
Thinking of doing some
ice fishing this weekend.

559
00:36:19,400 --> 00:36:20,629
Sorry to hear it.

560
00:36:20,720 --> 00:36:22,439
Interested?
No, sir.

561
00:36:22,520 --> 00:36:24,910
The only thing I ever
caught fishing in winter was a cold.

562
00:36:26,960 --> 00:36:28,360
Say, Chief, listen,
I been thinking

563
00:36:28,440 --> 00:36:30,432
about that fella
in the snow with the underpants.

