who is he?

574
00:36:52,160 --> 00:36:53,719
Ran his prints, nothing.

575
00:36:53,800 --> 00:36:55,678
Plus, it turns out
the car was stolen.

576
00:36:55,760 --> 00:36:56,910
Oh, yeah?
Yeah.

577
00:36:57,000 --> 00:36:58,116
Yeah,
over in Grand Forks.

578
00:36:58,200 --> 00:37:01,716
I called the local PD.
I'm just waiting on a callback.

579
00:37:03,920 --> 00:37:06,071
Any thoughts
there on Hess?

580
00:37:06,200 --> 00:37:08,396
No, not as such.

581
00:37:08,480 --> 00:37:11,552
The, um...
lady that Hess was with

582
00:37:11,640 --> 00:37:13,154
didn't get a good look
at the fella who killed him

583
00:37:13,240 --> 00:37:14,913
on account of all the blood in
her eyes, but...

584
00:37:15,000 --> 00:37:16,912
you know, we're checking
the knife for prints.

585
00:37:17,000 --> 00:37:19,117
Also, Bill's going
around to local stores

586
00:37:19,200 --> 00:37:22,193
to see if maybe the knife
was bought here in Bemidji.

587
00:37:24,600 --> 00:37:26,557
You'll make
a good chief one day.

588
00:37:26,680 --> 00:37:29,036
Me?

589
00:37:29,120 --> 00:37:31,476
